        <div class="msgUM"><a class="msgWhoName Sage" href="/users/Isiolia">Isiolia</a><div class="msgWhoTitle Sage">Sage</div></div><div class="msgAvatar"></div><div class="msgStar"><img src="http://common.zam.com/shared/s2.gif" alt="*"/><img src="http://common.zam.com/shared/s2.gif" alt="*"/><img src="http://common.zam.com/shared/s2.gif" alt="*"/><img src="http://common.zam.com/shared/s2.gif" alt="*"/></div><div class="msgWhoNum">6,926 posts</div>
        <div class="msgScore">
          Score: Good  
